    {
      "id": "prompt_1",
      "provider": "prompt",
      "name": "TakeUserInput",
      "config": {
        "instructions": [
          "Rank creators for trust and audience quality using ONLY the provided input JSON. Input shape: { interests: string[], creators: Creator[] }. Return ONLY a valid JSON object with EXACT top-level key \"ranked_creators\". Output schema: { \"ranked_creators\": [{ \"name\": \"string\", \"channelId\": \"string\", \"final_score\": 0.0, \"label\": \"High Trust Creator|Hidden Gem|Promising\", \"reason\": \"1-2 concise sentences\", \"tags\": [\"string\"] }] }. Rules: include every input creator exactly once; do not add creators; sort by final_score descending; final_score must be between 0 and 1; base analysis on comment quality, topic overlap, and engagement signals from input; if comments are sparse, use neutral assumptions and do not fabricate details. Forbidden: markdown headings, bullet lists, code fences, explanatory text before JSON, explanatory text after JSON. Specifically forbidden heading phrases: '# Analysis Summary', '## Key Findings', '## Ranking Rationale'."
        ],
        "parameters": {}
      },
      "ui": {
        "position": {
          "x": 460,
          "y": 200
        },
        "measured": {
          "width": 150,
          "height": 119
        },
        "nodeType": "default",
        "formDataValid": true
      },
      "input": [
